ed="T" n="0777b16"/><anchor n="T.50.2061.0777b16"/><head><date from-iso="+0618-06-21" key="j19469512052491" to-iso="+0907-06-06">唐</date><placeName key="PL000000028694">大溈山</placeName><persName key="A001984">靈祐</persName><ptr rend="display:none;" target="#n2662"/>傳</head><p><lb
ed="T" n="0777b17"/><persName key="A001984">釋靈祐</persName>，俗姓<name>趙</name>，祖、父俱<placeName key="PL000000018494"><placeName>福州</placeName><placeName>長溪</placeName></placeName>人也。<persName key="A001984">祐</persName>丱<lb
ed="T" n="0777b18"/>年戲于前庭，仰見瑞氣祥雲，徘徊盤欝，又<lb
ed="T" n="0777b19"/>如天樂清奏，真身降靈，衢巷諦觀，耆艾<ptr type="glossary" target="#g874"/>莫<lb
ed="T" n="0777b20"/>測。俄有華巔<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1576"/>之叟，狀類<placeName key="PL000000055418">罽賓</placeName>之人，謂家老<lb
ed="T" n="0777b21"/>曰：「此群靈眾聖標異。此<ref type="person" target="#A001984">童</ref>，佛之真子也，必<lb
ed="T" n="0777b22"/>當重光佛法。」久之，彈指數四而去。<persName key="A001984">祐</persName>以椎髻<lb
ed="T" n="0777b23"/>短褐，依本郡<persName key="A010526">法恒<roleName>律師</roleName></persName><ptr target="#n1580"/>執勞，每倍於役。<date key="j20096022009966" from-iso="+0790-01-01" to-iso="+0790-12-31">冠<lb
ed="T" n="0777b24"/>年</date>剃髮，三年具戒<ptr target="#n1581"/>。時有<placeName key="PL000000011520">錢塘</placeName>上士<persName key="A010527">義賓</persName>授其<lb
ed="T" n="0777b25"/>律科。及入<placeName key="PL000000014411">天<anchor xml:id="beg0777sgsz6"/>台<anchor xml:id="end0777sgsz6"/></placeName>，遇<persName key="A004127">寒山子</persName>於途中，乃謂<persName key="A001984">祐</persName><lb
ed="T" n="0777b26"/>曰：「千山萬水，遇<placeName key="PL000000019708">潭</placeName>即止。獲無價寶，賑䘏諸<lb
ed="T" n="0777b27"/>子。」<persName key="A001984">祐</persName>順途而念，危坐以思，旋造<placeName key="PL000000014664">國清寺</placeName>，遇<lb
ed="T" n="0777b28"/>異人<persName key="A009211">拾得</persName>申繫前意，信若合符<ptr target="#n2567"/>。遂詣<placeName key="PL000000019708">泐潭</placeName><lb
ed="T" n="0777b29"/>謁<persName key="A001897">大智<roleName>師</roleName></persName>，頓了祖意。<date notBefore-iso="+0816-08-13" key="j20193232020606" notAfter-iso="+0820-02-17"><name>元和</name>末</date>，隨緣<placeName key="PL000000028664">長沙</placeName>，因<pb ed="T" n="0777c" xml:id="T50.2061.0777c"/><lb
ed="T" n="0777c01"/>過<placeName key="PL000000028694">大溈山</placeName>，遂欲棲止。山與郡郭十舍<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1577"/>而遙，<lb
ed="T" n="0777c02"/>敻<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1449"/>無人煙，比為獸窟。乃雜猿猱之間，橡栗<lb
ed="T" n="0777c03"/>充食。浹旬<ptr type="glossary" target="#g287"/>，有山民見之，群信共營<name>梵</name>宇。時<lb
ed="T" n="0777c04"/><placeName key="PL000000027119">襄陽</placeName>連率<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1521"/><persName key="A010528">李景讓</persName><ptr target="#n1583"/>統攝<placeName key="PL000000029004">湘潭</placeName>，願預良緣，乃<lb
ed="T" n="0777c05"/>奏請山門號<placeName key="PL000000028706">同慶寺</placeName>。後相國<persName key="A003624">裴<roleName>公</roleName></persName>相親道<lb
ed="T" n="0777c06"/>合。<persName key="A001984">祐</persName>為遭<date from-iso="+0841-02-08" key="j20282682030170" to-iso="+0846-04-25"><name>會昌</name></date>之澄汰，又遇相國<persName key="A010529">崔<roleName>公</roleName>慎<lb
ed="T" n="0777c07"/>由</persName>崇重加<anchor xml:id="beg0777sgsz8"/>禮<anchor xml:id="end0777sgsz8"/>，以<date key="j20326672032667" when-iso="+0853-02-24"><name>大中</name>癸酉歲正月九日</date>盥<lb
ed="T" n="0777c08"/>漱畢，敷座瞑目而歸滅焉。享年八十三，僧<lb
ed="T" n="0777c09"/>臘五十九<ptr target="#n1582"/>。遷葬于<placeName key="PL000000028694">山</placeName>之右梔子園也。<placeName key="PLG00000000047">四鎮</placeName><lb
ed="T" n="0777c10"/><placeName key="PL000000047628">北庭</placeName>行軍<placeName key="PL000000045417">涇原</placeName>等州節度使、右散騎常侍<persName key="A010523">盧<lb
ed="T" n="0777c11"/>簡求</persName>為碑，<persName key="A009732">李商隱</persName>題額焉。</p>
